      <view class="good-img"><image src="https://i1.fuimg.com/708157/14662ff33149b189.png"></image></view>
      <view class="good-desc">
        <view class="good-title">绿宝瓶悦活蓄能新肌水 X1</view>
        <view class="good-sku">200ml</view>
